column2: b"@Crisopera1 There's alot more I won't share here. I saved all the letters. We met pre Internet. We wrote letters."

b"2020 has been a trip for me. I got closer to people I'd met pre pandemic & through them met equally awesome people. I've kept meeting awesome people who are smart silly & so very nice to me. I've been counseled countless times through my worst times. For that I am grateful for."
